TITLE: Configuring DRM License Servers in Shaka Player
DESCRIPTION: Sets up license server URLs for Widevine and PlayReady DRM systems using player.configure(). This is the basic configuration needed to play protected content.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shaka-project/shaka-player/blob/main/docs/tutorials/drm-config.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
player.configure({
  drm: {
    servers: {
      'com.widevine.alpha': 'https://foo.bar/drm/widevine',
      'com.microsoft.playready': 'https://foo.bar/drm/playready'
    }
  }
});
```

