TITLE: Removing Offline Content with Shaka Player
DESCRIPTION: Removes previously stored content from offline storage using the storage API. Takes the content's offline URI as input and supports progress reporting through a callback set during initialization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shaka-project/shaka-player/blob/main/docs/tutorials/offline.md#2025-04-17_snippet_6

