TITLE: Configuring Custom Headers for DRM
DESCRIPTION: Sets up custom headers for DRM license requests to the server.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shaka-project/shaka-player/blob/main/docs/tutorials/drm-config.md#2025-04-17_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
