TITLE: Configuring Custom Content ID Derivation for FairPlay in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to specify a custom init data transform for FairPlay content that uses custom signaling for the content ID. It's typically used with legacy Apple Media Keys.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shaka-project/shaka-player/blob/main/docs/tutorials/fairplay.md#2025-04-17_snippet_3

