TITLE: Breaking Changes in Shaka Player v4.0.0
DESCRIPTION: Major breaking changes including removal of deprecated features, configuration changes, and API updates that affect backward compatibility.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shaka-project/shaka-player/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
* Remove small/large gap config, always jump gaps
* manifest.dash.defaultPresentationDelay replaced by manifest.defaultPresentationDelay
* Configuration factories should be plain functions, not constructors
* addTextTrack() replaced by addTextTrackAsync()
* TrackLabelFormat and FailReasonCode moved to shaka.ui.Overlay namespace
* Storage.store() now returns AbortableOperation instead of Promise
* Removed getStoreInProgress()
* Uint8ArrayUtils.equal replaced by BufferUtils.equal
* SegmentIndex.destroy() replaced by synchronous release()
* SegmentIterator.seek() replaced by SegmentIndex.getIteratorForTime()
* SegmentIndex.merge() made private
* AbrManager plugins must implement playbackRateChanged()
* Cue.spacer replaced by lineBreak
* IUIElement plugins must have release() method
```

