SOURCE: https://github.com/shaka-project/shaka-player/blob/main/docs/style.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
X = class {
  doSomethingFast() {
    X.doSomething(this.fast);
  }
  doSomethingSlow() {
    X.doSomething(this.slow);
  }
  static doSomething(target) {
    // a lot of math
    // 
    result = ...
    target.doSomething(result);
  }
};
```

